1.title: Ang bahay ni Tita
1.plot: The show mainly revolved around the friendship between Rhodman, Jeff and Kurt. The trio are about to transfer to an apartment, which is in an ownership dispute between Tita Malou and Don Roman. Jeff, a culinary student; Rhodman, a college varsity player; and Kurt, a musician, will now embark on a journey of slowly discovering the different characters in their new barangay, starting from their landlady and her twin daughters, Jingle and Jinky, together with their helper Yaya Nene. There's also hilarious Don Roman, a local gambling chief with his bodyguards Brando and ...

2.title: Ang carinderia
2.plot: Jeff, Rhodman and Kurt decided to eat at the nearby eatery managed by Don Roman's niece, Princess and her bestfriend Marie. Kap's eagerness to clean up the Barangay is strengthen by the help of his another loyal tanod, Tiny.

3.title: Ang picnic
3.plot: Tita Malou and her family decided to have a picnic at a nearby park where Kurt encounters a mysterious guitar girl named Vienna. An unexpected rain ruined the picnic until Rhodman suggested a better idea.

imdb.plot outline: Barangay Teegang is a Filipino social media sitcom created by CJ Santos. The show will premiere on Tee Radio on September 1, 2017. The show is primarily centered on 2 story arcs. The first arc centers on the friendship of Jeff, Rhodman and Kurt, who was forced to transfer to a new apartment owned by Tita Malou and Don Roman who both claimed ownership to the house. Jeff is a culinary student who is friends with Rhodman, a varsity player and Kurt, a musician. The second story arc centers on the triangle love affair of Tita Malou, a widow and mother of Jinky and Jingle. Don Roman, a local gambling chief and Kap, the barangay captain. The kindness of Jeff, awkwardness of Kurt and comic relief of Rhodman is the main focus of the show.
